<p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1.中国战“疫”进入新阶段，新冠疫情，变与不变，做好自己健康的第一责任人。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240305/1709647912774016348.jpg" title="1709647912774016348.jpg" alt="c5850d449a517843b1f983405e97a1c3.jpg" width="150" height="146" style="width: 150px; height: 146px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; widows: 1;">2.寒假及春节假期坚持少聚集、勤洗手、常通风、戴口罩等卫生习惯。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; widows: 1;">3.加强寒假及春节假期健康管理，严格健康异常报告、就医、检测，主动配合执行疫情防控各项要求。</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; widows: 1; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">4.学生应积极接种新</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; widows: 1; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">冠病毒疫苗，尽快实现“应接必接”。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; widows: 1;">5.学生及家长非必要不出行、不出境、不前往中高风险地区所在区市。寒假期间返乡探亲、过节需主动向学校报备，返乡途中做好个人防护。</span></p><p><br/></p>